en_2554766_0	The levy on telecommunications has been increased by 5 percent from Wednesday.
en_2554766_1	The 20 percent levy that was introduced in the 2014 budget has now been increased to 25 percent.
en_2554766_2	Director General of the Telecommunication Regulatory Commission, Anusha Palpita said that there will be no change in the 10 percent levy charged on internet and broadband.
